<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Text decoration properties</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="text_decoration_properties.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div>
        Trees are vital for life on Earth as they provide oxygen, improve air quality,
        conserve water, preserve soil, and support biodiversity. They act as natural 
        air filters by absorbing carbon dioxide and releasing oxygen, helping combat 
        climate change. Trees also offer shade, reduce urban heat, and serve as habitats
        for countless species. Beyond environmental benefits, they promote human well-
        being by creating peaceful surroundings and enhancing the beauty of our planet.
    </div>
